      "text": "Electric Substantive Rules - Chapter 25 - 25.192 - Transmission Service Rates\n\nHome Rules and Laws Substantive Chapter 25 - Electric Transmission Service Rates\n\nNavigation\n\nPublic Utility Commission\n\nMenu\n\n# Electric Substantive Rules - Chapter 25\n\n## §25.192 - Transmission Service Rates.\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments to §25.192 as Approved at the November 30, 2022 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendments to §25.192 as Approved at the August 4, 2022 Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments to §§25.101, 25.174, and 25.192 as Approved at the June 9, 2016 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendments to §§25.101, 25.174, and 25.192 as Approved at the February 11, 2016 Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendment to §25.192 and §25.501 as Approved at the March 7, 2012 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendment to §25.192 and §25.501 as Approved at the December 8, 2011, Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendment to §25.192 as Approved at the July 30, 2010 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendment to §25.192 as Approved at the January 29, 2010 Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments, New Rules and Repeals Consistent with the New Market Design Developed by ERCOT as Approved at the May 24, 2001 Open Meeting and Published in the Texas Register on June 15, 2001\n\nProposed Amendments, New Rules and Repeals to Revise the Commission's Transmission Rules Consistent with the New Market Design Developed by ERCOT as Published in the Texas Register on March 9, 2001\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendments to §§25.192, 25.193, 25.194, 25.198 and 25.204 as published in the Texas Register on October 15, 1999\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments to §§25.192, 25.193, 25.194, 25.198 and 25.204 as Approved at the December 1, 1999 Open Meeting and Published in the Texas Register on December 24, 1999",
      "highlights": [
        "Electric Substantive Rules - Chapter 25 - 25.192 - Transmission Service Rates\n\nHome Rules and Laws Substantive Chapter 25 - Electric Transmission Service Rates\n\nNavigation\n\nPublic Utility Commission\n\nMenu\n\n# Electric Substantive Rules - Chapter 25\n\n## §25.192 - Transmission Service Rates.\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments to §25.192 as Approved at the November 30, 2022 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendments to §25.192 as Approved at the August 4, 2022 Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments to §§25.101, 25.174, and 25.192 as Approved at the June 9, 2016 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendments to §§25.101, 25.174, and 25.192 as Approved at the February 11, 2016 Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendment to §25.192 and §25.501 as Approved at the March 7, 2012 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendment to §25.192 and §25.501 as Approved at the December 8, 2011, Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendment to §25.192 as Approved at the July 30, 2010 Open Meeting\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendment to §25.192 as Approved at the January 29, 2010 Open Meeting\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments, New Rules and Repeals Consistent with the New Market Design Developed by ERCOT as Approved at the May 24, 2001 Open Meeting and Published in the Texas Register on June 15, 2001\n\nProposed Amendments, New Rules and Repeals to Revise the Commission's Transmission Rules Consistent with the New Market Design Developed by ERCOT as Published in the Texas Register on March 9, 2001\n\nProposal for Publication of Amendments to §§25.192, 25.193, 25.194, 25.198 and 25.204 as published in the Texas Register on October 15, 1999\n\nOrder Adopting Amendments to §§25.192, 25.193, 25.194, 25.198 and 25.204 as Approved at the December 1, 1999 Open Meeting and Published in the Texas Register on December 24, 1999"
